{"id":1208647568,"question_id":72,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 months, 1 week","timestamp":1710894902,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1208647568/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"45.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int minDistance(String word1, String word2) {\n        int m = word1.length();\n        int n = word2.length();\n        int[][] dp = new int[m+1][n+1];\n\n        for(int i=0;i<=m;i++){\n            dp[i][0] = i;\n        }\n\n        for(int j=0;j<=n;j++){\n            dp[0][j] = j;\n        }\n\n\n        for(int i=1;i<=m;i++){\n            for(int j = 1;j<=n;j++){\n                if(word1.charAt(i-1) == word2.charAt(j-1))\n                    dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1];\n                else\n                //Replace:dp[i-1][j-1] | Delete: dp[i-1][j]| Insert: dp[i][j-1]\n                    dp[i][j] = Math.min(dp[i-1][j], Math.min(dp[i-1][j-1], dp[i][j-1])) + 1;\n            }\n        }\n        return dp[m][n];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
